 “Answer speed is up by 15% in the new contact centers, and the RMG technology has been a major contribution to that. The centers now look state-of-the-art and this has absolutely helped us win new business.”  

Global Technology Director for CSC, Mark Rowland
 

 







“We also utilize our displays to further improve employee morale, recognizing excellent performances, and congratulating our team members on their achievements. It’s a great way to keep our workforce happy and subsequently, our customers who then receive an even better level of service.” 

Peter Cassalete, Allianz Global Assistance 

 







“Firstly, it expands our message frequency and effectiveness. Traditional posters provide one message; a digital screen delivers far bigger frequency of message from the same footprint.”  

James Munnelly, Bank of Ireland 

 








 

 

 

 

 

 

 


 




 
 





 



 



 
 
 

 
 
 




 



 

