RMG Networks Holding Corp Company Profile

 
			

Get an in-depth profile of RMG Networks Holding Corp, including a general overview of the company's business and key management, as well as employee data and location and contact information.









 


IndustryAdvertising
SectorServices
Employees161
Equity TypeORD


RMG Networks Holding Corporation is a holding company. The Company is a provider of enterprise-class digital signage solutions. The Company, through a suite of products, software, software-embedded hardware, maintenance and content service, installation services, and third-party displays, delivers intelligent visual communication solutions to its clients. As an integrated digital signage solution provider across the globe, the Company conducts its operations through RMG Enterprise Solutions business unit. The Company's solutions portfolio consists of solutions for intelligent contact center, visual internal communications, visual supply chain and consumer-facing retail, financial services, higher education, and hospitality applications. Its product components include Enterprise Software, Media Players/Smart Digital Appliances, Design Studio and Design Studio Lite, InView, Subscription Content Services and Electronic Displays.


Contact Information


